BEEF BACK RIBS (Full Rack) (Regular) - Juicy, tender, and fall-of-the-bone! The new hit of the hood - glazed beef back ribs. Generously seasoned with our house-made rub mix and glazed with our Signature or Sweet&Spicy BBQ sauces. Includes a complimentary 3oz BBQ Sauce and pickled jalapeño peppers.


*ALLERGEN CONTENT*: Sauce and Glaze may contain FISH and MUSTARD SEEDS

*Allergen warning*: Sauce may contain traces of FISH and MUSTARD seeds.
